    Jenkins jobs, often called projects, are the core unit of work for CI/CD processes

3. Jenkins Freestyle Project
 Key Job Types in Jenkins:
  1a. Pipeline: Recommended for complex, multi-stage workflows (defined via Jenkinsfile)
  1b. Freestyle Project: A basic, GUI-configured task for simple operations
  1c. Multibranch Pipeline: Automatically creates jobs for every branch in a repository
  1d. Maven Project: Specialized for building projects with pom.xml files

